The '''Baia Wind Farm''' is an under construction wind power project in [[Baia, Tulcea|Baia]], [[Tulcea County]], [[Romania]]. It will have 14 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.financiarul.com/articol_17532/blue-investments-va-aloca-60-milioane-de-euro-pentru-un-parc-eolian-in-judetul-tulcea.html |title=Blue Investments va aloca 60 milioane de euro pentru un parc eolian in judetul Tulcea |date=2008-11-21 |work=Blue Investments va aloca 60 milioane de euro pentru un parc eolian in judetul Tulcea |publisher=Financiarul |language=Romanian |accessdate=2009-02-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090108203256/http://www.financiarul.com/articol_17532/blue-investments-va-aloca-60-milioane-de-euro-pentru-un-parc-eolian-in-judetul-tulcea.html |archivedate=2009-01-08 |df= }}</ref> with a nominal output of around 2.5 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] which will deliver up to 35 MW of power, enough to power over 21,000 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$84 million.

