The '''Eolus Vind Wind Farm''' is a proposed wind power project in [[Constanţa County]], [[Romania]]. It will have 15 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref>[http://www.standard.ro/articol_58512_12/eolus_vind_intra_cu_15_mil______pe_eolian.html Eolus Vind intra pe eolian {{ro}}]</ref> with a nominal output of around 2 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] which will deliver up to 50 MW of power, enough to power over 19,800 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$23 million.

